{
  "id": "adv_event_2112_01_01",
  "title": "クリスマスの過ごし方",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "みなさーん！　今日のライブ、楽しかったですかー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks everybody‚ are you having fun today?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.3993540764,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 5.6060206095
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "今年も残り一ヶ月！\nうちらは最後まで駆け抜けていきます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s just one month left in the year!\nWe’re going to keep running to the end!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.6060206095,
      "endTime": 11.0431632678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 11.229829963
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "これからも応援よろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please keep supporting us!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.229829963,
      "endTime": 14.379331096,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 14.5926644483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEでしたー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We are TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5926644483,
      "endTime": 16.6670408407,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 17.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "今日のステージもすっごく盛り上がったね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today’s show was another lively one!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.8,
      "endTime": 22.2981248856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 22.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "せやなぁ\nなんだか最近ファンとの距離が近くなった気ぃするわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right.\nI have the feeling we’ve got closer to the fans lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.4666666667,
      "endTime": 28.333333333299997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "これも星見プロに移籍した影響かもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That might be another effect of moving to Hoshimi Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.5333333333,
      "endTime": 32.6395917733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 32.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロから移籍して、環境が大きく変わって\n今年は怒濤の一年やったなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moving from Van Productions was a big change of environment.\nThis was a turbulent year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8333333333,
      "endTime": 39.7136019899,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 39.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、もうすぐクリスマスなんだよね\nこの時期はいつももっと忙しかった気がするけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ Christmas is coming up.\nAround this time of year‚ I remember us being way busier than we are right now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9333333333,
      "endTime": 49.0579694837,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 49.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロにいた頃は\n姫野さんがえげつない量の仕事を入れてたからなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When we were with Van Productions‚\nHimeno-san always piled up an inhumane amount of work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.2666666667,
      "endTime": 54.6447960593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 54.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロではうちらに負担が掛かり過ぎないように\n{user}さんが調整してるらしいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At Hoshimi Productions‚ {user}-san arranges work so\nwe don’t get overloaded.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8333333333,
      "endTime": 61.5621837696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 61.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "そういう所にも事務所の違いが出るんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s another aspect where the differences between agencies show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7333333333,
      "endTime": 65.6574375947,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 65.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "私はもっと忙しくても大丈夫だけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wouldn’t mind being busier…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8666666667,
      "endTime": 69.0666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ、クリスマスはいつも忙しかったから\nたまにはゆっくりしてもええんとちゃう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ Christmas was always a busy time‚\nisn’t it good to take it easy sometimes?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2666666667,
      "endTime": 75.6023763705,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 75.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば24日は仕事が入ってないんだよね\nクリスマスイブが丸一日オフなんて初めてじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of Christmas‚ we don’t have any work on the 24th.\nIsn’t this the first time we ever had the whole of Christmas Eve off?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.8,
      "endTime": 85.0001599122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 85.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんはイブは何して過ごすん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How are you going to spend Christmas Eve‚ Rui-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2,
      "endTime": 88.1787302494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "仕事があると思ってたから何も予定は入れてないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I didn’t schedule anything because I figured we’d have work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3666666667,
      "endTime": 92.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 92.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "うちも同じや。すみれちゃんは？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m the same. What about you‚ Sumire-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.7333333333,
      "endTime": 95.6999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "私も何も考えてなかったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I haven’t thought of anything to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.9666666667,
      "endTime": 99.7800207297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスイブ、どうしようかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What shall we do with Christmas Eve?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0666666667,
      "endTime": 106.2116042296,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4333.333333300005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "すみれ？　一人で何をしていますの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire? What are you doing here alone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4,
      "endTime": 109.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、すずちゃん。ちょっと考え事してたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Suzu-chan. I was just thinking about something.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1333333333,
      "endTime": 114.6816043218,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "今年のイブはオフなんだけど\n何して過ごそうかと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve got this Christmas Eve off‚\nso I was wondering how to spend it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9,
      "endTime": 120.5963271808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "？　普通に過ごしたらいいんじゃないんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Couldn’t you just spend it like normal?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7666666667,
      "endTime": 124.72743755980001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "子役の頃からイベントや撮影とかあって、アイドルに\nなってからもグランプリとかがあったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since my time as a child actress‚ I always had photoshoots and events.\nAnd since I became an idol‚ there have been things like the Grand Prix.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.9,
      "endTime": 132.50374986650002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2112_01_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "この時期に丸一日予定が空いてるのは久しぶりで\n何をしたらいいのか分からないんだよね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s been a long time since I had a whole day with nothing booked at this time of year.\nI have no idea what to do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.7,
      "endTime": 140.0420619342,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
