      "text": "すずちゃんはクリスマスはいつもどう過ごしてるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan‚ how do you usually spend Christmas?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2666666667,
      "endTime": 144.0913959186,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
